20x613/filters:focal(857x517:1183x843)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/63989923/elon_musk_tesla_3036.0.jpg 920w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/-XAobt_AIV0TAsTLikTFuwqbbwc=/0x0:2040x1360/1220x813/filters:focal(857x517:1183x843)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/63989923/elon_musk_tesla_3036.0.jpg 1220w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/LZGWTW5MhTb7ToslpacVI3p0BI4=/0x0:2040x1360/1520x1013/filters:focal(857x517:1183x843)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/63989923/elon_musk_tesla_3036.0.jpg 1520w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/MpTuZJa6arhmZDHPhTGtrMt16Pw=/0x0:2040x1360/1820x1213/filters:focal(857x517:1183x843)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/63989923/elon_musk_tesla_3036.0.jpg 1820w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/amvj8mJQNXKHd8j8Vr52bJ_AFYk=/0x0:2040x1360/2120x1413/filters:focal(857x517:1183x843)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/63989923/elon_musk_tesla_3036.0.jpg 2120w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ZrpUUXRyt8R30mZKSo15nFJXQmE=/0x0:2040x1360/2420x1613/filters:focal(857x517:1183x843)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/63989923/elon_musk_tesla_3036.0.jpg 2420w\" alt=\"\" data-upload-width=\"2040\" /></picture></span></span></figure>\r\n<div class=\"c-entry-content \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px; position: relative; color: #424242; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<p id=\"JtpXdt\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">Horses were a somewhat unexpected theme at Tesla&rsquo;s annual shareholder meeting. After CEO Elon Musk suggested that owning a gas car would be the equivalent of using a horse to get around, a Tesla shareholder asked Musk if the company&rsquo;s announced pickup would have enough go power to haul her horse. &ldquo;I didn&rsquo;t mean to insult horses earlier,&rdquo; Musk replied. &ldquo;I love horses.&rdquo; (Yes, the planned pickup could haul her horse.)</p>\r\n<p id=\"w90Qyg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">The shareholder meeting had some ups and downs &mdash; from a member of animal rights group PETA asking about vegan steering wheels to a discussion about Model 3 demand. The meeting comes at a time when Tesla&rsquo;s stock price is at a two-year low after falling almost continuously throughout 2019. The company suffered one of its&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: #e5127d; transition: color 0.1s ease 0s, background-color 0.1s ease 0s, fill 0.1s ease 0s; border-bottom: 1px solid currentcolor;\" href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2019/4/24/18514427/tesla-q1-2019-loss-model-3-elon-musk-earnings\">worst quarterly losses ever</a>to start the year, has faced new scrutiny about the safety of its&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: #e5127d; transition: color 0.1s ease 0s, background-color 0.1s ease 0s, fill 0.1s ease 0s; border-bottom: 1px solid currentcolor;\" href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2019/5/16/18627766/tesla-autopilot-fatal-crash-delray-florida-ntsb-model-3\">Autopilot driver assistance feature</a>, and endured&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: #e5127d; transition: color 0.1s ease 0s, background-color 0.1s ease 0s, fill 0.1s ease 0s; border-bottom: 1px solid currentcolor;\" href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2019/5/16/18627746/tesla-fire-battery-software-update-model-s-x\">questions about recent battery fires</a>.</p>\r\n<div id=\"OxpNmV\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; left: 0px; width: 739.922px; height: auto; position: relative;\">\r\n<div class=\"p-scalable-video\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 416.203px 0px 0px; position: relative; height: 0px; width: 739.922px; background-color: #000000;\"><iframe style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: 416.203px; position: absolute; top: 0px; width: 739.922px;\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Va5i42D13cI?rel=0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id=\"bT7NRE\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">Musk spent nearly an hour and a half updating shareholders on the company, and taking questions as well. Here are some of the highlights (besides, obviously, the horse chat):</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"YAUUAE\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: Heroic, \'Arial Narrow\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: calc(1.95312em); line-height: 1.2; margin: 0px 0px 0.6rem; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase;\">DEMAND</h2>\r\n<p id=\"dKSxbi\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">&ldquo;I want to be clear: there is not a demand problem,&rdquo; Musk said at the top of his presentation Tuesday. &ldquo;Absolutely not.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p id=\"igDBNj\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">Wall Street analysts and industry experts have<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: #e5127d; transition: color 0.1s ease 0s, background-color 0.1s ease 0s, fill 0.1s ease 0s; border-bottom: 1px solid currentcolor;\" href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2019/2/15/18213953/teslas-moder-3-new-costumers-europe-china\">&nbsp;questioned the demand</a>&nbsp;for Tesla&rsquo;s cars in 2019. This is largely because Tesla&rsquo;s cars are still fairly expensive. They&rsquo;re no longer eligible for the full federal EV tax credit, and the cheapest $35,000-version of the car&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: #e5127d; transition: color 0.1s ease 0s, background-color 0.1s ease 0s, fill 0.1s ease 0s; border-bottom: 1px solid currentcolor;\" href=\"https://electrek.co/2019/05/14/tesla-model-3-increases-price/\">basically</a>&nbsp;never&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: #e5127d; transition: color 0.1s ease 0s, background-color 0.1s ease 0s, fill 0.1s ease 0s; border-bottom: 1px solid currentcolor;\" href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2019/4/12/18307583/tesla-original-plan-tesla-model-3-base-model\">materialized</a>, meaning every one of Tesla&rsquo;s vehicles is sold&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">above</em>&nbsp;the average transaction price in the US.</p>\r\n<div class=\"c-float-right\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 36.9844px; padding: 0px; float: right; width: 332.953px;\">\r\n<aside id=\"bCMZGT\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><q style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: Heroic, \'Arial Narrow\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 2em; font-style: italic; line-height: 1; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 1rem 1.25rem 0px 0px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #e5127d; display: block; position: relative;\">&ldquo;I WANT TO BE CLEAR: THERE IS NOT A DEMAND PROBLEM.&rdquo;</q></aside>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id=\"jw9Qr8\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">Even Musk said in January that &ldquo;the inhibitor&rdquo; to buying a Tesla is &ldquo;affordability&rdquo; because &ldquo;people literally don&rsquo;t have the money to buy the car.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p id=\"vPDOlM\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">But Musk argued at the meeting that there is no demand problem, and that Tesla is still finding new customers. He said 90 percent of orders coming in are from customers who aren&rsquo;t holding a reservation for the Model 3, without giving specifics.</p>\r\n<p id=\"U0bChM\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">&ldquo;Sales have far exceeded production, and production has been pretty good,&rdquo; Musk said. &ldquo;So, we&rsquo;re actually doing well, and we have a decent shot at a record quarter on every level,&rdquo; he added, echoing a point he made in&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: #e5127d; transition: color 0.1s ease 0s, background-color 0.1s ease 0s, fill 0.1s ease 0s; border-bottom: 1px solid currentcolor;\" href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2019/5/23/18637076/elon-musk-tesla-record-deliveries-good-chance-this-quarter-email-leak\">a recently-leaked all-staff email</a>. &ldquo;If not, it&rsquo;s going to be very close.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p id=\"IsmBau\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">Tesla started shipping Model 3s to China and Europe at the beginning of the year. Both markets represent huge opportunities for the company, but issues with each rollout had some analysts worried. Tesla has also cut back production of the Model S and Model X, though it did just&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: #e5127d; transition: color 0.1s ease 0s, background-color 0.1s ease 0s, fill 0.1s ease 0s; border-bottom: 1px solid currentcolor;\" href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2019/4/24/18513899/tesla-model-s-x-range-upgrade-270-325-miles-supercharger-200kw\">announce upgraded versions of those cars</a>&nbsp;that might be more attractive to buyers.</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"vfnVYO\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: Heroic, \'Arial Narrow\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: calc(1.95312em); line-height: 1.2; margin: 0px 0px 0.6rem; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase;\">MAXWELL TECHNOLOGIES ACQUISITION</h2>\r\n<p id=\"8Uw7J0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">Tesla recently completed a months-long process of buying up&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: #e5127d; transition: color 0.1s ease 0s, background-color 0.1s ease 0s, fill 0.1s ease 0s; border-bottom: 1px solid currentcolor;\" href=\"https://electrek.co/2019/05/16/tesla-completes-maxwell-acquisition-battery-technology/\">battery tech company Maxwell Technologies</a>. There&rsquo;s been a ton of speculation as to what, exactly, Tesla believes Maxwell has to offer, but the company had been tight-lipped while the deal was still closing.</p>\r\n<p id=\"8oBmyj\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">In response to a question at Tuesday&rsquo;s shareholder meeting, though, Musk finally gave the beginnings of an answer, calling the acquisition &ldquo;quite strategic.&rdquo; He&rsquo;s saving full details for when Tesla holds a &ldquo;battery and powertrain investor day&rdquo; (a follow-on event to the recent &ldquo;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: #e5127d; transition: color 0.1s ease 0s, background-color 0.1s ease 0s, fill 0.1s ease 0s; border-bottom: 1px solid currentcolor;\" href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2019/4/22/18510828/tesla-elon-musk-autonomy-day-investor-comments-self-driving-cars-predictions\">autonomy investor day</a>&rdquo;), but Musk said Maxwell had developed some &ldquo;very important technologies&rdquo; that he believes will make it cheaper and easier to quickly scale up production of lithium-ion battery cell production.</p>\r\n<p id=\"Gqzi03\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">That could be a huge boon for Tesla, as Musk also said at the meeting that the biggest thing standing in the way of the company&rsquo;s growth is battery production.</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"yvcXBD\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: Heroic, \'Arial Narrow\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: calc(1.95312em); line-height: 1.2; margin: 0px 0px 0.6rem; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase;\">TESLA PICKUP TRUCK</h2>\r\n<p id=\"oNhFDb\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">Musk has expressed his love for the forthcoming Tesla pickup truck again and again, and so it&rsquo;s no surprise he repeated that sentiment at the shareholder meeting. &ldquo;I think it&rsquo;s the coolest car I&rsquo;ve ever seen, to be frank,&rdquo; he said. Musk echoed previous claims about how the truck will look &ldquo;cyberpunk&rdquo; and like it&rsquo;s come from a &ldquo;sci-fi movie.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p id=\"ulGWjg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">Tesla didn&rsquo;t reveal any images of the truck Tuesday, save for a very indistinguishable teaser. But the pickup truck will be revealed sometime later this summer, &ldquo;hopefully,&rdquo; Musk said, which clarified previous comments about Tesla&rsquo;s plan to unveil the vehicle. Musk reiterated that the Tesla pickup will be more functional than a Ford F-150 but also a better sports car than a basic Porsche 911. (He&rsquo;s also said he wants it to start at&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: #e5127d; transition: color 0.1s ease 0s, background-color 0.1s ease 0s, fill 0.1s ease 0s; border-bottom: 1px solid currentcolor;\" href=\"https://electrek.co/2019/06/02/tesla-pickup-truck-price-f150-elon-musk/\">less than $50,000</a>.) Also, it&rsquo;s tough enough to haul a horse.</p>\r\n<p id=\"VUDy1J\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">&ldquo;We&rsquo;re trying to create something new and it&rsquo;s, it&rsquo;s not just basically a copy of the form factor of everything else,&rdquo; he said. &ldquo;But you still want it to be great. It&rsquo;s very hard. This is a very hard thing.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"x3AhB9\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: Heroic, \'Arial Narrow\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: calc(1.95312em); line-height: 1.2; margin: 0px 0px 0.6rem; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase;\">TESLA... MINING COMPANY?</h2>\r\n<p id=\"ffVEwW\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">The pickup truck, as well as the other products in Tesla&rsquo;s pipeline, like the second-generation Roadster and the Tesla Semi, aren&rsquo;t going to come to fruition unless Tesla can find a way to build more batteries, Musk said. Part of the plan to make that happen is to keep opening Gigafactories around the world. But even that will only go so far to help meet the company&rsquo;s hunger for batteries, and so Musk said he&rsquo;s considering moving Tesla further into the lithium-ion battery supply chain.</p>\r\n<div class=\"c-float-left\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 36.9844px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 332.953px;\">\r\n<aside id=\"bcwoU0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><q style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: Heroic, \'Arial Narrow\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 2em; font-style: italic; line-height: 1; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 1rem 1.25rem 0px 0px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #e5127d; display: block; position: relative;\">&ldquo;WE MIGHT GET INTO THE MINING BUSINESS.&rdquo;</q></aside>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id=\"Z2UTYr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">&ldquo;We might get into the mining business, I don&rsquo;t know, maybe a little bit at least,&rdquo; he said. &ldquo;We&rsquo;ll do whatever we have to to ensure that we can scale at the fastest rate possible.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p id=\"VVkeMy\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">Tesla&rsquo;s whole thing is vertical integration &mdash; the Gigafactory in Nevada is designed to ultimately be able to take raw materials in one end and and roll cars out the other, though it&rsquo;s still&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: #e5127d; transition: color 0.1s ease 0s, background-color 0.1s ease 0s, fill 0.1s ease 0s; border-bottom: 1px solid currentcolor;\" href=\"https://www.theverge.com/transportation/2018/11/30/18118451/tesla-gigafactory-nevada-video-elon-musk-jobs-model-3\">a ways away from that goal</a>. Getting into mining could certainly help complete that vision, while also securing materials in&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: #e5127d; transition: color 0.1s ease 0s, background-color 0.1s ease 0s, fill 0.1s ease 0s; border-bottom: 1px solid currentcolor;\" href=\"https://qz.com/africa/1178440/apple-tesla-volkswagen-to-pay-more-for-cobalt-batteries-if-dr-congo-ups-mining-taxes/\">what is turning out</a>&nbsp;to be a&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: #e5127d; transition: color 0.1s ease 0s, background-color 0.1s ease 0s, fill 0.1s ease 0s; border-bottom: 1px solid currentcolor;\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2019-06-03/lithium-miners-australia-chile-see-riches-as-ev-battery-makers\">pretty volatile market</a>&nbsp;as more electric vehicles get built every year.</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"ehizLJ\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: Heroic, \'Arial Narrow\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: calc(1.95312em); line-height: 1.2; margin: 0px 0px 0.6rem; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase;\">TESLA INSURANCE</h2>\r\n<p id=\"QzETv9\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">Musk announced on a conference call in April that Tesla is going to&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: #e5127d; transition: color 0.1s ease 0s, background-color 0.1s ease 0s, fill 0.1s ease 0s; border-bottom: 1px solid currentcolor;\" href=\"https://electrek.co/2019/04/24/tesla-launch-insurance-program-elon-musk/\">start offering insurance to its customers</a>, and said it &ldquo;will be more compelling than anything else&rdquo; on the market, since the company has more direct access to its cars&rsquo; (and therefore its drivers&rsquo;) data. But in response to a question about what is holding up the offering, Musk said Tesla has &ldquo;a small acquisition that we need to complete, and a bit of software to write.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p id=\"9oOIwR\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">He didn&rsquo;t specify what company Tesla might be buying, but reassured shareholders that &ldquo;it won&rsquo;t be long before&rdquo; Tesla starts offering insurance.</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"XTUdsi\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: Heroic, \'Arial Narrow\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: calc(1.95312em); line-height: 1.2; margin: 0px 0px 0.6rem; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase;\">SOLAR ROOF</h2>\r\n<p id=\"Hg9sef\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">Tesla unveiled its&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: #e5127d; transition: color 0.1s ease 0s, background-color 0.1s ease 0s, fill 0.1s ease 0s; border-bottom: 1px solid currentcolor;\" href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2016/10/28/13463236/tesla-solar-roof-battery-new-elon-musk\">solar roof tiles all the way back in 2016</a>, right around the time that the company was buying Solar City. They still aren&rsquo;t much of a commercial product. They&rsquo;re being deployed in eight states, Musk said Tuesday, but he added that making them is &ldquo;quite a hard problem.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p id=\"tczzah\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">Tesla is working on a third iteration of the tiles, which Musk said he&rsquo;s &ldquo;really excited about,&rdquo; and that the company has &ldquo;a shot&rdquo; at bringing the cost of a full solar roof down to that of a normal, shingled version plus the cost of utilities.</p>\r\n<p id=\"cgVGLB\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">Drew Baglino, Tesla&rsquo;s vice president of technology, said his team &ldquo;is super motivated by that goal, and we think we can achieve it,&rdquo; before clarifying that they are &ldquo;laser focused&rdquo; on matching that cost.</p>\r\n<div class=\"c-float-right\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 36.9844px; padding: 0px; float: right; width: 332.953px;\">\r\n<aside id=\"N0ucjN\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><q style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: Heroic, \'Arial Narrow\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 2em; font-style: italic; line-height: 1; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 1rem 1.25rem 0px 0px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #e5127d; display: block; position: relative;\">&ldquo;THERE&rsquo;S A LOT OF COMPLEXITY IN PARKING LOTS.&rdquo;</q></aside>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id=\"zzLCck\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">&ldquo;I&rsquo;ve had a number of meetings with with Drew, where I&rsquo;m like banging the table, [saying] &lsquo;Damn it, we&rsquo;ve got to achieve this,&rsquo;&rdquo; Musk added, to laughs from the room.</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"EZ83vv\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: Heroic, \'Arial Narrow\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: calc(1.95312em); line-height: 1.2; margin: 0px 0px 0.6rem; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase;\">ADVANCED SUMMON</h2>\r\n<p id=\"6OuPDn\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">Tesla has been nearing the rollout of a feature called &ldquo;Advanced Summon&rdquo; for a while now, where owners will be able to tap a button in the company&rsquo;s app and summon their car to them. The car will navigate parking lots and pedestrians all by itself.</p>\r\n<p id=\"bMjagO\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">Musk offered an update on the rollout of the feature Tuesday. &ldquo;We&rsquo;re making steady improvements to it. It&rsquo;s close to being amazing. It&rsquo;s not quite there but it&rsquo;s close,&rdquo; he said. &ldquo;There&rsquo;s a lot of complexity in parking lots.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<aside id=\"8PV1Bx\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><q style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: Heroic, \'Arial Narrow\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 2em; font-style: italic; line-height: 1; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 1rem 1.25rem 0px 0px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #e5127d; display: block; position: relative;\">&ldquo;I&rsquo;M SOMETIMES A LITTLE OPTIMISTIC ABOUT TIMEFRAMES.&rdquo;</q></aside>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id=\"LAzpgi\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">Musk said he wants to make sure Advanced Summon is safe before rolling it out widely. &ldquo;We don&rsquo;t want to like, run someone over,&rdquo; he said. &ldquo;The threshold is, is it more convenient to summon your car, or walk your car, and if it&rsquo;s more convenient to walk, summon is not that useful. So it has to move reasonably fast.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p id=\"9SyVmC\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">Advanced Summon was supposed to be available by now, according to Musk himself. But the Tesla CEO shied from putting a time frame on a full rollout. &ldquo;I&rsquo;m sometimes a little optimistic about timeframes,&rdquo; he said. &ldquo;It&rsquo;s time you knew.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"DVUPYP\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: Heroic, \'Arial Narrow\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: calc(1.95312em); line-height: 1.2; margin: 0px 0px 0.6rem; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase;\">MUSK VERSUS THE MEDIA</h2>\r\n<p id=\"ea5BHX\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">Musk is known for hectoring the media&rsquo;s coverage of Tesla, and by the end of this year&rsquo;s shareholder meeting it had become a persistent topic that threaded through multiple questions.</p>\r\n<p id=\"Do9plL\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">When asked how Tesla can make sure its status as a &ldquo;true Great American success story gets told,&rdquo; Musk responded that &ldquo;it&rsquo;s very distressing, it makes me sad. I&rsquo;m not sure what to do about it.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p id=\"UV7rzg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">Musk said Tesla does provide &ldquo;rebuttals&rdquo; to stories it perceives to be negative, but that the responses get &ldquo;buried.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p id=\"t04EnX\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">&ldquo;It&rsquo;s the most crazy disinformation campaign I&rsquo;ve ever seen,&rdquo; Musk said.</p>\r\n<p id=\"axJNqV\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">One shareholder proposed Musk turn to media moguls like Michael Bloomberg and Arianna Huffington to find a better way to get the company&rsquo;s message out, which Musk said was a &ldquo;good idea.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p id=\"fk9X3w\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">But, Musk added that be believes there&rsquo;s been &ldquo;quite a few negative articles in&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Bloomberg</em>.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p id=\"8cr1VD\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">Another shareholder asked Musk why he doesn&rsquo;t spend money on marketing or advertising, something the company famously avoids.</p>\r\n<p id=\"BiJFcP\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">&ldquo;Currently, we are selling more cars than we can make,&rdquo; Musk said. &ldquo;Spending money on advertising would make things worse financially.&rdquo; Musk also added that he believes there&rsquo;s &ldquo;just too much trickery in advertising.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"um9tM1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: Heroic, \'Arial Narrow\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: calc(1.95312em); line-height: 1.2; margin: 0px 0px 0.6rem; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase;\">WELCOME, ROBYN DENHOLM</h2>\r\n<p id=\"FlS5MR\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">Robyn Denholm was appointed&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: #e5127d; transition: color 0.1s ease 0s, background-color 0.1s ease 0s, fill 0.1s ease 0s; border-bottom: 1px solid currentcolor;\" href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2018/11/8/18074800/tesla-new-chair-2018-robyn-denholm-elon-musk\">late last year to replace Musk</a>&nbsp;as chair of Tesla&rsquo;s board of directors, and she has given statements about the company in the time since. But this was the first time she&rsquo;s stood up in front of a crowd and represented the company so fully, and so this was the public&rsquo;s first good chance to see how she handles herself at Tesla. (She recently completed the process of stepping down from&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: #e5127d; transition: color 0.1s ease 0s, background-color 0.1s ease 0s, fill 0.1s ease 0s; border-bottom: 1px solid currentcolor;\" href=\"https://www.afr.com/business/telecommunications/telstra-reveals-cfo-replacement-for-robyn-denholm-20190409-p51chy\">her other company, Telstra</a>.)</p>\r\n<p id=\"wRwvWv\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">Her first address to the company&rsquo;s shareholders was a mix of humor and reinforcement. She joked about having to run through the &ldquo;boring&rdquo; part of the night (taking votes on shareholder proposals) before getting to Musk&rsquo;s presentation and the Q&amp;A session, which she said was &ldquo;always a highlight of the stockholders meeting.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p id=\"2sXCEa\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">But Denholm was sincere, too, about the support the company&rsquo;s gotten despite myriad struggles. &ldquo;I would like to start today&rsquo;s meeting by thanking you, our investors, our shareholders, for the tremendous support that you&rsquo;ve given Tesla not just over the last 12 months, but also over the last many years,&rdquo; she said. &ldquo;When you&rsquo;re changing the world, and many industries in the process, you need to have a certain amount of intestinal fortitude as an investor. And when I speak to many of you, as shareholders, you have that in spades.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p id=\"L95tVo\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\">&ldquo;I am incredibly honored to be your chair,&rdquo; she said.</p>\r\n<p id=\"SWqUsu\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">Correction</span></em><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">: This article mistakenly stated that Tesla&rsquo;s cars aren&rsquo;t eligible for the federal EV tax credit. They are no longer eligible for the full tax credit, but buyers can still receive half the $7,500 value until July 1st, and half again until the end of the year. The article has been updated.</em></p>\r\n</div>','Gonna take my Tesla to the old town road...',4),(8,'Everything we think we know about the Pixel 4, from Google’s Pixel 4 reveal',9,'2019-06-13',NULL,1,'<h3 id=\"luzfPo\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: Heroic, \'Arial Narrow\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: calc(1.5625em); line-height: 1.2; margin: 0px 0px 0.6rem; padding: 0px; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase; color: #424242; background-color: #ffffff;\">DUAL CAMERAS</h3>\r\n<p id=\"pyYKTy\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px; color: #424242; background-color: #ffffff;\">Let&rsquo;s start with the biggest one: there are two cameras very clearly positioned in the middle of that bulbous square popping out of the back of the phone.<em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</em>Google has made a point in recent years of differentiating the Pixel by sticking with a single rear camera, yet still managing to pull off impressive tricks like portrait mode shots. But just about every high-end competitor now has two (<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: #e5127d; transition: color 0.1s ease 0s, background-color 0.1s ease 0s, fill 0.1s ease 0s; border-bottom: 1px solid currentcolor;\" href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2019/3/1/18245446/samsung-galaxy-s10-plus-android-phone-review-price-specs-features\">if not</a>&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: #e5127d; transition: color 0.1s ease 0s, background-color 0.1s ease 0s, fill 0.1s ease 0s; border-bottom: 1px solid currentcolor;\" href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2019/4/10/18285123/huawei-p30-pro-review-periscope-camera-zoom-android-phone\">more</a>) cameras on the back of their flagship phones, and there are some things &mdash; like focal length &mdash; that just can&rsquo;t be precisely recreated using software magic.</p>\r\n<div id=\"3v5pUO\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #424242; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<div class=\"SandboxRoot env-bp-350\" style=\"max-height: 10000px; direction: ltr; background: 0px 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4; font-family: Helvetica, Roboto, \'Segoe UI\', Calibri, sans-serif; color: #1c2022; white-space: initial; position: relative;\" data-twitter-event-id=\"0\">\r\n<div id=\"twitter-widget-0\" class=\"EmbeddedTweet EmbeddedTweet--cta EmbeddedTweet--mediaForward media-forward js-clickToOpenTarget js-tweetIdInfo tweet-InformationCircle-widgetParent\" lang=\"en\" style=\"overflow: hidden; cursor: pointer; border: 0px; border-radius: 5px; max-width: 520px; position: relative;\" data-click-to-open-target=\"https://twitter.com/madebygoogle/status/1138876305158500353\" data-iframe-title=\"Twitter Tweet\" data-scribe=\"page:tweet\" data-tweet-id=\"1138876305158500353\" data-twitter-event-id=\"1\">\r\n<article class=\"MediaCard\r\n           MediaCard--mediaForward\r\n           \r\n           customisable-border\" dir=\"ltr\" data-scribe=\"component:card\">\r\n<div class=\"MediaCard-media\" style=\"position: relat